which aims to set up a free trade zone in the sub-region by the
year 2000.
</P>
<P>
Mbuende said Madagascar has also shown interest to join, but
no formal letter has been handed in.
</P>
<P>
SADC treaty provides for admission of new members with close
consideration to the laid-down procedures, he added.
</P>
<P>
SADC was formed in 1992 with its aim of establishing a common
market for southern Africa. 
