<P>
"I am going to hold talks with Pakistani Prime Minister Nawaz
Sharif in New York. Indo-Pakistani relations are improving. We are
hopeful that all our aspirations for improved bilateral relations
would be fulfilled," he said in West Bengal of northeastern India.
