<HEADLINE> Premier Li Urges Preparedness for Typhoon Amber </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
FUZHOU, August 30 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Premier Li Peng has
expressed great concern about preparations people in east China's
Fujian Province are making to combat the eminent arrival of
Typhoon Amber.
</P>
<P>
