passed on the premier's instructions for local people to make
every effort to reduce losses resulting from the typhoon, and to
be especially prepared to control possible flooding of the local
Minjiang River.
</P>
<P>
Jiang conveyed the premier's cordial greetings to the local
people, and instructed residents in coastal areas in the predicted
path of the typhoon to be fully prepared in order to keep losses
of life and property to an absolute minimum. 
</P>
</TEXT>
