having free falling. The stock exchange index in Hong Kong fell by 5
percent on Friday, and that of Bangkok by 4.1 percent, while those
in Manilla, Jakarta, and Kuala Lumpur fell Thursday by 9.3 percent,
4.5 percent and 4.2 percent. This is not only a fall, but a krach.
</P>
<P>
