Prime Minister Hun Sen, Foreign Minister Ung Hout and acting head
of state in his absence, Chea Sim, at the airport, is a good sign.
</P>
<P>
ASEAN is giving full attention to its mission led by Indonesian
Foreign Minister Ali Alatas to achieve its objective.
</P>
<P>
On Cambodia's entry into ASEAN, Abdullah said that it all
depended on the situation in that country. It is ASEAN's hope
that Cambodia could join the regional grouping as soon as
possible, he added.  
