<HEADLINE> Uruguayan Infant Mortality Drops </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MONTEVIDEO, August 29 (Xinhua) -- Uruguayan Infant mortality
rate dropped to 15.3 per 1,000 during the first half of 1997
compared with the figure of 17.6 during the same period in 1996, a
